Imager-QRCode version 0.01

INSTALLATION

First, You must install libqrencode-1.0.1.tar.gz
(via. http://megaui.net/fukuchi/works/qrencode/index.en.html)


Second, to install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install


Alternatively, to install with Module::Build, you can use the following commands:

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build
    ./Build test
    ./Build install


